how it's done?
-Okay.

21:45.721 --> 21:47.681
(cheering)

21:49.183 --> 21:51.268
Luke:
Whoa! Oh!

21:51.268 --> 21:52.353
(laughing)

21:56.982 --> 21:58.984
Just bone, already.

21:58.984 --> 22:01.570
Yeah, all this foreplay's
giving us blue balls.

22:11.664 --> 22:13.207
Smile.

22:16.168 --> 22:17.461
-Here you go.
-Thanks.

22:17.461 --> 22:18.838
No worries.

22:20.214 --> 22:22.383
Hey, this is cool.

22:22.383 --> 22:25.094
You know, chilling with you.

22:25.094 --> 22:26.262
Yeah.

22:30.808 --> 22:32.434
I don't think Megan's
into me anymore.

22:34.228 --> 22:35.896
No!

22:35.896 --> 22:37.231
No, she loves you.

22:37.231 --> 22:39.275
She's just...

22:39.275 --> 22:40.609
She's going through something.

22:42.319 --> 22:46.490
Well, you were going through
something last summer too.

22:46.490 --> 22:48.242
I don't get it,
is it something that I did?

22:48.242 --> 22:50.286
No. Not at all.

22:50.286 --> 22:51.829
Well, then what is it?

22:54.540 --> 22:57.376
I broke up with you
when I found out
that Megan liked you.

22:57.376 --> 23:00.462
Don't look so surprised.

23:00.462 --> 23:04.091
You liked her,
it was pretty obvious.

23:04.091 --> 23:06.427
You guys were just destined
to be together.

23:10.055 --> 23:12.349
(relaxing rock music playing)

23:18.898 --> 23:21.275
Sit right there
and drink this soda.

23:21.275 --> 23:22.693
I think your liver
needs a reboot.

23:24.945 --> 23:26.572
(siren chirps)

23:26.572 --> 23:30.576
Oh... Hide the booze,
the cops are here!

23:30.576 --> 23:32.620
woman over radio:
Hands in the air! Nobody move!

23:32.620 --> 23:34.038
Please don't arrest me.

23:34.038 --> 23:35.831
Brent:
Uh, what's your name?

23:35.831 --> 23:37.416
That's not a real cop,
you idiot.

23:37.416 --> 23:40.336
(laughs) What's your name,
sweetheart?

23:40.336 --> 23:41.670
I'm Officer Bunny.

23:41.670 --> 23:44.173
-(guests murmuring)
-Who's the birthday boy?

23:44.173 --> 23:46.800
Uh, right here, Officer Bunny.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.427
Take him downtown
for questioning.

23:48.427 --> 23:49.762
Do a strip search.

23:49.762 --> 23:52.640
Probe him
with your night stick.

23:52.640 --> 23:57.519
I hear you've been
very, very bad.

23:57.519 --> 23:59.980
You have no idea.

23:59.980 --> 24:03.359
Yeah, you guys,
you can go in the Airstream.

24:05.194 --> 24:06.862
Take as much time as you need.

24:10.532 --> 24:14.828
♪ My blood is a sermon
that burns upon contact ♪

24:14.828 --> 24:16.664
♪ Reminds you of wounds ♪

24:16.664 --> 24:18.582
♪ That you thought
you'd forgotten... ♪

24:42.606 --> 24:45.150
Hi, Trevor,
it's Megan Landry calling.

24:45.150 --> 24:47.528
Again.

24:47.528 --> 24:49.029
I got your letter.

24:49.029 --> 24:50.823
We need to talk.

25:03.127 --> 25:04.753
Officer Bunny:
Ooh!

25:04.753 --> 25:06.505
Happy birthday, sweetheart.

25:06.505 --> 25:08.424
(Luke laughs awkwardly)

25:11.301 --> 25:13.679
-Are you ready to get excited?
-Luke: I'll just... okay.

25:13.679 --> 25:15.639
Officer Bunny:
Hmm.

25:15.639 --> 25:17.683
(Officer Bunny continues,
voice muffled)

25:23.522 --> 25:27.317
Luke: You have taken
so many hits for Megan.

25:27.317 --> 25:29.028
I mean...

25:29.028 --> 25:30.362
(scoffs)

25:30.362 --> 25:32.031
