25:32.031 --> 25:34.992
and taking the fall
for the sex tape.

25:34.992 --> 25:37.411
Yeah.

25:37.411 --> 25:40.372
She's my sister.

25:40.372 --> 25:41.999
I know that she
would do the same for me.

25:45.085 --> 25:47.379
Maybe I do give up
too much, though.

25:47.379 --> 25:49.673
But loyalty's everything to me.

25:49.673 --> 25:51.467
Do you ever regret it?

25:53.969 --> 25:55.179
Never.

25:59.725 --> 26:01.101
I still think about you.

26:06.023 --> 26:07.149
The hell?

26:07.149 --> 26:08.692
I'm-I'm... Hold on.

26:08.692 --> 26:11.361
Wait, I'm sorry, I thought
that you were feeling it.

26:11.361 --> 26:13.947
You thought wrong.

26:13.947 --> 26:15.240
We should go.

26:19.787 --> 26:20.829
-Okay, girls, ready?
-Yeah.

26:20.829 --> 26:22.790
Okay. So you throw...

26:22.790 --> 26:24.958
hip, right...

26:24.958 --> 26:26.752
hip... Ooh, nice!

26:26.752 --> 26:29.505
(laughs) You step out, twirl.

26:29.505 --> 26:31.507
Twirl...
You got it, you got it.

26:31.507 --> 26:33.175
And then you do
the genie thing.

26:33.175 --> 26:35.469
Ow! You guys look so good!

26:35.469 --> 26:37.137
No, get in here, Megan!

26:37.137 --> 26:38.764
Uh, no, I can't dance.

26:38.764 --> 26:40.724
Come on. Just follow me.

26:42.434 --> 26:44.186
Follow me.
I'm sure you'll get it.

26:44.186 --> 26:45.145
Like this.

26:47.106 --> 26:48.857
No, no, you gotta control
your hips more.

26:48.857 --> 26:51.110
Looking good, it's looking good.

26:51.110 --> 26:52.694
Like your body's made
of caramel.

26:52.694 --> 26:54.530
Wait. Why caramel?

26:54.530 --> 26:56.907
Uh, because it's sweet
and stretchy?

26:56.907 --> 26:58.700
(laughing)

26:58.700 --> 27:00.160
This is kind of fun.

27:00.160 --> 27:01.328
Mm-hmm.

27:01.328 --> 27:03.247
Fun and hot.

27:03.247 --> 27:05.707
It's not the worst way
to get somebody to notice you.

27:08.710 --> 27:11.964
-(guys laughing)
-Brent: There's the man.

27:11.964 --> 27:13.423
Give us all the deets.

27:13.423 --> 27:14.716
You get a lap dance?

27:14.716 --> 27:17.636
She danced on more
than just my lap.

27:17.636 --> 27:19.179
That's what I'm talking about!

27:19.179 --> 27:22.182
Us Chambers men, we get it done!

27:22.182 --> 27:23.725
Come on, dude, you're my hero!

27:23.725 --> 27:25.602
Brent: You see that?
Did you see that?

27:25.602 --> 27:27.312
Total stud.

27:27.312 --> 27:28.564
(keying rapidly)

27:45.330 --> 27:47.249
Ned? I'm done.

27:49.668 --> 27:52.379
(buzzer sounds, lock clicks)

27:52.379 --> 27:54.172
This is really nice.

27:54.172 --> 27:56.967
This is my shrine to the past.

27:56.967 --> 27:59.511
Oh, that-- that was my baby.

27:59.511 --> 28:01.346
-Can I?
-Yeah, please.

28:04.558 --> 28:06.768
It never made it
to market, 'cause...

28:06.768 --> 28:08.437
the company fired me
and shelved it.

28:12.149 --> 28:15.235
I grew up poor, you know.

28:15.235 --> 28:18.697
I taught myself coding
and climbed the ladder.

28:18.697 --> 28:21.909
So when I got fired,
I thought my life was over.

28:21.909 --> 28:24.703
But now I make my own rules.

28:24.703 --> 28:26.580
I'm in control.

28:26.580 --> 28:29.625
Yeah, that's what I want.

28:29.625 --> 28:32.461
My boyfriend thinks
I'm obsessed.

28:32.461 --> 28:35.422
Mostly he just doesn't
really get it.

28:35.422 --> 28:38.800
He hasn't found that thing
that he loves yet.

28:38.800 --> 28:41.595
He'll probably just end up
joining the family business.

28:41.595 --> 28:44.765
Ah, the Chambers dynasty.

28:44.765 --> 28:46.391
Well, I wouldn't call it that.

28:47.851 --> 28:50.437
They would.

28:50.437 --> 28:52.648
His father thinks
he's above the law

28:52.648 --> 28:54.608
and everyone should
bend to his will.

28:54.608 --> 28:57.319
Fellow like that
doesn't have a lot of time
for other opinions.

28:59.738 --> 29:03.116
Yeah, well... Luke's...
he's not like that.

29:04.451 --> 29:05.994
Maybe not yet.

29:05.994 --> 29:09.706
But... the apple doesn't
usually fall far. (chuckles)

29:12.542 --> 29:16.296
(Christina Aguilera
playing "Genie in a Bottle")

29:16.296 --> 29:18.340
♪ My body's saying let's go ♪

29:18.340 --> 29:21.802
♪ Oh-whoa ♪

29:21.802 --> 29:23.845
♪ But my heart is saying no ♪

29:23.845 --> 29:25.263
Yo, Chambers.

29:25.263 --> 29:27.766
-guy 1: Ohh!
-guy 2: Nasty!

29:27.766 --> 29:29.351
Is that Megan?

29:29.351 --> 29:30.602
Tim:
"Landry Gone Wild."

29:30.602 --> 29:32.646
Eric: Did not know
she could move like that.

29:32.646 --> 29:34.439
Brent: I didn't know
she had that body.

29:36.108 --> 29:37.484
Yes!

29:37.484 --> 29:39.486
Hey, Jeff, you're a lucky guy.

29:39.486 --> 29:41.029
(guys laughing)

29:42.489 --> 29:44.241
Brent:
Yes!

29:44.241 --> 29:45.951
Oh, I love her!

29:45.951 --> 29:47.035
(Megan laughs)

29:47.035 --> 29:49.246
Watch and learn, boys.

29:49.246 --> 29:50.414
(guy whoops)

29:50.414 --> 29:51.415
Oh, yeah!

29:54.626 --> 29:55.877
That's my girl.

29:58.797 --> 30:00.298
You're so friggin' hot.

30:00.298 --> 30:01.675
Parker:
I know.

30:01.675 --> 30:06.722
♪ Waiting for someone
who needs me ♪

30:06.722 --> 30:09.725
♪ My heart is beating
at the speed of light ♪

30:09.725 --> 30:12.352
♪ But that don't mean
it's gonna be tonight ♪

30:12.352 --> 30:15.856
♪ Baby, baby, baby ♪

30:15.856 --> 30:17.774
Brent:
Yes! Oh, yeah.

30:17.774 --> 30:19.609
♪ Oh-whoa-oh ♪

30:19.609 --> 30:21.695
Don't you all need
a drink or something? Come on!

30:21.695 --> 30:22.738
Get it, Luke!

30:22.738 --> 30:24.281
It's your birthday!

30:24.281 --> 30:27.284
(cheering)

30:27.284 --> 30:29.619
♪ But my heart is saying no ♪

30:29.619 --> 30:32.831
♪ Do you wanna
be with me, baby? ♪

30:32.831 --> 30:34.916
(over headset)
♪ There's a price to pay ♪

30:34.916 --> 30:37.794
♪ I'm a genie in a bottle ♪

30:37.794 --> 30:40.714
♪ You gotta rub me
the right way ♪

30:40.714 --> 30:42.382
(banging on door)

30:46.970 --> 30:48.805
I know about St. Barts.

30:48.805 --> 30:50.182
About Lisa.

31:00.025 --> 31:01.485
How did you find out?

31:01.485 --> 31:04.196
Trevor.

31:04.196 --> 31:06.364
His visit makes
a ton more sense now.

31:09.868 --> 31:12.370
I started to tell you a hundred
different times about Lisa--

31:12.370 --> 31:16.666
But you didn't. You know,
you have told so many lies,

31:16.666 --> 31:18.502
and they're all
to make you look good.

31:18.502 --> 31:20.462
I'm telling you the truth
about Lisa--

31:20.462 --> 31:22.839
You've been lying
since the day you got here.

31:22.839 --> 31:25.884
Lying about your past,
lying about our friendship.

31:25.884 --> 31:27.177
Everything!

31:29.513 --> 31:31.640
I've read the police report.

31:31.640 --> 31:35.352
It was your idea to go swimming.

31:35.352 --> 31:36.770
And then she drowned.

31:39.731 --> 31:40.899
No.

31:43.068 --> 31:45.237
Lisa jumped in the water
on her own.

31:47.739 --> 31:52.244
She was drunk, upset.

31:52.244 --> 31:54.579
I went after her to make sure
that she was okay.

31:54.579 --> 31:56.623
And then she was gone.

31:58.750 --> 32:00.377
It was the worst night
of my life.

32:02.796 --> 32:03.755
I should've told you.

32:06.091 --> 32:07.509
I wish I had.

32:09.469 --> 32:11.638
(relaxing music in background)

32:11.638 --> 32:13.765
I'm not sure you're gonna be
able to top this next year.

32:13.765 --> 32:15.308
Hey! You're not supposed
to be in here.

32:15.308 --> 32:16.726
First rule of birthday cake is--

32:16.726 --> 32:18.812
What? Don't talk about
birthday cake or something?

32:18.812 --> 32:20.647
Yes.

32:20.647 --> 32:22.357
Okay, fine, screw it.

32:29.322 --> 32:31.032
Whoa, this is so good.

32:31.032 --> 32:32.325
-Did you make this?
-Mm-hmm.

32:34.077 --> 32:35.996
This has been...

32:35.996 --> 32:37.873
like an almost perfect day.

32:39.708 --> 32:41.251
You know I like
getting an A in everything.

32:44.129 --> 32:47.340
Is there something else
that could make it more perfect?

32:54.639 --> 32:56.558
You know, I've missed
hanging with you this summer.

32:59.144 --> 33:00.896
Like just the two of us.

33:03.690 --> 33:05.150
Yeah, me too.

33:13.575 --> 33:16.161
Oh, crap, I'm sorry, I'm...

33:16.161 --> 33:18.246
I'm like, I'm gonna be sick.

33:24.294 --> 33:25.503
Hi.

33:28.924 --> 33:31.009
You couldn't come
to the Plunge, so...

33:31.009 --> 33:32.761
I'm bringing the Plunge to you.

33:35.305 --> 33:37.682
'99 will make the annual
collection after all.

33:39.517 --> 33:41.686
Thank you. It's sweet.

33:41.686 --> 33:44.064
Did you and Isabella have fun?

33:46.399 --> 33:48.318
Honestly, you were the...

33:48.318 --> 33:49.819
you're the only thing
that was on my mind.

33:52.906 --> 33:55.242
You know, I miss you.

33:56.826 --> 33:57.744
I miss us.

33:59.621 --> 34:01.248
These last few days
really sucked.

34:03.959 --> 34:05.085
I miss you too.

34:08.046 --> 34:09.339
Let's start fresh.

34:09.339 --> 34:11.341
Okay?

34:11.341 --> 34:12.926
Let's catch up.

34:12.926 --> 34:14.344
Tell me about your day.
What'd you get up to?

34:18.265 --> 34:20.141
I have a better idea.

34:43.748 --> 34:44.791
Hey.

34:48.795 --> 34:50.297
You've been kind of quiet today.

34:52.299 --> 34:54.342
Just enjoying the show.

34:56.636 --> 35:01.600
It's been really educational,
in a crappy kind of way.

35:01.600 --> 35:02.642
I'm confused.

35:05.353 --> 35:10.275
I saw it before, a while back.

35:10.275 --> 35:12.861
But then it felt
like things had changed.

35:14.696 --> 35:17.115
I thought we had something good.

35:18.742 --> 35:20.452
What are you talking about?

35:22.454 --> 35:23.913
You and Luke.

35:25.165 --> 35:26.958
It's so obvious.

35:26.958 --> 35:30.503
He's the one you wanna
be with, not me.

35:33.256 --> 35:34.716
It's his birthday.

35:34.716 --> 35:39.512
Every time I turned around today
you were with him.

35:39.512 --> 35:44.684
And when you weren't with him,
you were talking about him.

35:44.684 --> 35:46.895
Worrying about him.

35:46.895 --> 35:50.231
He's my best friend
and he just got dumped.

35:50.231 --> 35:52.150
Yeah. Lucky for you.

35:52.150 --> 35:53.860
That's not fair.

35:53.860 --> 35:58.114
What's not fair is me being
used as your practice run.

35:59.991 --> 36:01.493
That's not what it's like.

36:04.454 --> 36:09.000
You can lie to yourself, Megan,
but you can't lie to me.

36:14.130 --> 36:15.131
We're done.

36:28.186 --> 36:30.230
Why should I believe you, Iz?

36:30.230 --> 36:32.357
I never lied about us.

36:32.357 --> 36:36.861
I tried to be a better friend
to you than I was to Lisa.

36:36.861 --> 36:39.030
