the one on the sex tape,

36:39.030 --> 36:41.700
to protect you.

36:41.700 --> 36:43.368
The whole time,

36:43.368 --> 36:46.996
even after everything that
happened on New Year's Eve,

36:46.996 --> 36:48.957
I had your back.

36:48.957 --> 36:50.542
Did you?

36:50.542 --> 36:53.336
Or were you just covering
your ass after what you did?

36:53.336 --> 36:57.632
I think that you went back
to the cabin on New Year's,

36:57.632 --> 37:00.635
and you killed Luke,
just like you killed Lisa.

37:10.562 --> 37:13.565
I haven't laughed
that hard in a long time.

37:13.565 --> 37:16.776
I will never look at a pie
the same way again.

37:16.776 --> 37:19.946
I've got that wine
that Wayne Bright sent
from his vineyard.

37:19.946 --> 37:22.490
Steve:
Sounds great.

37:22.490 --> 37:24.284
Hey! How was the party?

37:24.284 --> 37:26.453
It was really fun.

37:26.453 --> 37:29.414
Yeah? The birthday boy
didn't overdo it, I take it?

37:29.414 --> 37:31.624
Nope. Brent had his back.

37:31.624 --> 37:33.460
Well, if everyone had
a good time

37:33.460 --> 37:36.629
and the cops didn't come,
that is a hit in my book.

37:36.629 --> 37:38.006
-Steve: Mm.
-(glasses clink)

37:40.550 --> 37:41.634
What'd you guys do?

37:41.634 --> 37:43.428
Got dinner, saw a movie.

37:47.974 --> 37:49.100
We...

37:50.477 --> 37:52.187
It was really funny.

37:54.856 --> 37:55.899
Cool.

38:00.820 --> 38:02.113
Um...

38:02.113 --> 38:04.407
Did that look like a,
you know...?

38:04.407 --> 38:05.575
A date?

38:05.575 --> 38:08.161
This one time at band camp...

38:08.161 --> 38:09.829
(Debbie laughing)

38:09.829 --> 38:13.458
Oh, yeah. Yeah, it's on.

38:13.458 --> 38:14.375
(laughs)

38:18.296 --> 38:20.799
I'm really glad you came over.

38:20.799 --> 38:23.676
We needed time together, alone.

38:25.678 --> 38:28.723
I'm sorry, I've been kind of
weird the last few days.

38:28.723 --> 38:30.141
That's okay.

38:32.435 --> 38:36.022
Just... you and Isabella...

38:36.022 --> 38:39.359
when it comes to money,
you guys are on a completely
different planet than I am.

38:39.359 --> 38:41.653
It's not your fault,
it's just...

38:41.653 --> 38:43.154
sometimes it's hard.

38:45.824 --> 38:47.033
I get that.

38:49.077 --> 38:51.287
But that doesn't matter.

38:55.250 --> 38:57.043
Anyway, I just...

38:57.043 --> 39:01.297
I really appreciate
how you let me be me.

39:01.297 --> 39:02.715
Even when I suck.

39:06.010 --> 39:07.387
You couldn't suck if you tried.

39:19.357 --> 39:21.317
Megan, something...

39:21.317 --> 39:24.571
something happened
at the Plunge today.

39:24.571 --> 39:26.197
What kind of something?

39:30.243 --> 39:32.620
Me and Isabella...

39:32.620 --> 39:35.498
we weren't fighting, you know.

39:35.498 --> 39:37.458
We were...

39:37.458 --> 39:40.587
It was like old times.
You know, we were cool.

39:40.587 --> 39:42.380
Okay, you're kind of
freaking me out.

39:42.380 --> 39:43.506
What happened?

39:54.559 --> 39:55.685
She kissed me.

39:55.685 --> 39:57.645
And, uh...

39:57.645 --> 39:59.814
Look, I-I-- Look,
I shut it down right away

39:59.814 --> 40:01.399
and I drove her right home.

40:04.068 --> 40:05.320
I can't believe her.

40:08.573 --> 40:09.699
I thought you should know.

40:26.174 --> 40:28.927
Hey, sweetheart.
This is a nice surprise.

40:28.927 --> 40:31.763
I, um... I just heard something.

40:34.140 --> 40:35.558
And I think you should know.

40:51.824 --> 40:53.534
We need to talk.

40:55.203 --> 40:57.163
Where did you get those?

40:57.163 --> 40:58.706
They were in the Airstream.

41:04.629 --> 41:06.005
Did Isabella give them to you?

41:08.508 --> 41:10.009
Is that Luke's blood?

41:13.805 --> 41:15.139
You think I killed him.

41:16.808 --> 41:18.226
I love you.

41:19.268 --> 41:21.688
There's nothing
I won't do for you.

41:22.647 --> 41:24.232
But I need to know
what happened.

41:25.274 --> 41:26.901
And what if you don't
like what you hear?

41:35.660 --> 41:37.412
(somber theme song playing)
